Syntax: CLASS variable < (options) > . . . < variable < (options) > > < / global-options > ;

The CLASS statement names the classification variables to be used in the scale regression model. These
variables enter the analysis not through their values, but through levels to which the unique values are mapped.

Syntax: NLOPTIONS options ; 

